===Etymology===
First attested in the late 14th century. First attested in reference to an unintended pregnancy in 1932. From {{etyl|enm|en}}, from {{etyl|fro|en}} {{term|accident|lang=fro}}, from {{etyl|la|en}} {{m|la|accidēns}}, present active participle of {{m|la|accidō||happen}}; from {{term|ad||to|lang=la}} + {{m|la|cadō||fall}}. See {{term|cadence|lang=en}}, {{term|case|lang=en}}.

===Pronunciation===
